title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 85-2.12 - Service of documents

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 85-2.12 - Service of documents

State Regulations
(a) The service
of documents upon parties in a certification proceeding shall be governed by
section
4.3
(b)(2)
of this

Title. (b) Unless a party otherwise
requests, the names and addresses of parties shall be placed on the secretary's
service list. Notes
